text:
Feeling nostalgic?

Can visit to Poh Kim at Harbourfront Centre. This shop has been here for decades. It used to be a popular shop. In recent years with the rise of tv cables including Netflix, less and lesser people will opt for the old DVDs.

Classic selections. I wish the store had more arrangements to categories or actors/actresses because even the shop manager couldn't find an actress and I understand why. Still got movies I love! Went in for about 10 minutes or so just looking through and got the titles I needed.
